---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { CarrouselImage } from "@/components/carrouselImage";

const ImagePfl = [
  "images/pfl-1.jpg",
  "images/pfl-2.jpg",
  "images/pfl-3.jpg",
  "images/pfl-4.jpg",
  "images/pfl-5.jpg",
  "images/pfl-6.jpg",
];
const ImageInca = [
  "images/inca-1.jpg",
  "images/inca-2.jpg",
  "images/inca-3.jpg",
  "images/inca-4.jpg",
  "images/inca-1.jpg",
  "images/inca-2.jpg",
  "images/inca-3.jpg",
  "images/inca-4.jpg",
];
const ImageAda = [
  "images/ada-1.jpg",
  "images/ada-2.jpg",
  "images/ada-4.jpg",
  "images/ada-5.jpg",
  "images/ada-3.jpg",
  "images/ada-1.jpg",
  "images/ada-2.jpg",
  "images/ada-4.jpg",
  "images/ada-5.jpg",
  "images/ada-3.jpg",
];
---

<Layout>
  <a
    href=""
    class="hover:bg-color2 hover:text-white hover:border-color2 transition duration-300 ease-in-out font-medium uppercase text-sm tracking-wide shadow border border-neutral-300 text-color2 fixed py-4 px-7 bottom-5 right-5 sm:bottom-8 sm:right-12 bg-white rounded-lg z-10"
    >Let's Talk</a
  >
  <div class="pt-6 px-4 md:px-12 md:pt-12">
    <div class="text-md font-bold uppercase md:text-2xl tracking-widest">
      <a href="index">Juan Miguel Mifflin</a>
    </div>
    <div class="md:flex justify-between uppercase md:pt-1 text-xs md:text-sm">
      <div class="text-neutral-500 tracking-widestmore">
        curiosity, work and design
      </div>
      <div class="flex font-bold gap-6 tracking-widest mt-6 md:mt-0">
        <a
          class="hover:bg-color2 hover:text-white transition duration-100 ease-in-out md:px-2 rounded-md"
          href="#">Resume</a
        >
        <a
          class="hover:bg-color2 hover:text-white transition duration-100 ease-in-out md:px-2 rounded-md"
          href="#">works</a
        >
        <a
          class="flex hover:bg-color2 hover:text-white transition duration-100 ease-in-out md:px-2 rounded-md fill-red-600 hover:fill-red-300"
          href="#"
          ><span>Things That I</span>
          <span class="pl-1 self-center">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class=""
              width="14px"
              height="14px"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                d="M14 20.408c-.492.308-.903.546-1.192.709-.153.086-.308.17-.463.252h-.002a.75.75 0 01-.686 0 16.709 16.709 0 01-.465-.252 31.147 31.147 0 01-4.803-3.34C3.8 15.572 1 12.331 1 8.513 1 5.052 3.829 2.5 6.736 2.5 9.03 2.5 10.881 3.726 12 5.605 13.12 3.726 14.97 2.5 17.264 2.5 20.17 2.5 23 5.052 23 8.514c0 3.818-2.801 7.06-5.389 9.262A31.146 31.146 0 0114 20.408z"
              ></path></svg
            ></span
          ></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr class="mt-3 md:mb-10 md:mx-12" />
  <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 pt-12">
    <div class="md:flex gap-12">
      <div
        class="mb-6 md:mb-0 md:grid content-center basis-1/2 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img src="images/yo-animado.gif" alt="" />
      </div>
      <div class="basis-1/2 grid content-center">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-6xl font-black pb-8"
        >
          hi! my name is <br class="hidden lg:inline" /><span
            class="text-color2">Juan Miguel Mifflin</span
          >
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg font-light text-neutral-500 max-w-3xl">
          <span class="font-bold text-neutral-800"
            >and I'm a designer and UX/UI expert with 15 years of experience.</span
          > My most distinctive trait is my curiosity, which I consider the driving
          force behind creativity and learning. <span class="hidden lg:inline">
            What I love most about my work is blending this curiosity with my
            passion for design. I also lead diverse teams and constantly learn
            from them, fusing creativity with strategic communication.</span
          > Currently, I am designing, and implementing digital projects within the
          following brands: Peru For Less, Inca Expert, and Latin America For Less.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="my-20 mx-6 sm:mx-12" />
  <div
    class="text-color2 text-2xl sm:text-4xl px-16 font-bold mx-auto max-w-7xl"
  >
    I believe I've been fortunate to work on a wide variety of projects, learn
    from them, and collaborate with a diverse range of individuals. Below, I
    share some of the projects I've had the privilege to work on :)
  </div>
  <hr class="my-20 mx-6 sm:mx-12" />

  <div class="px-8 sm:px-12 lg:px-24">
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-20 font-bold">
      My Process
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-nowrap gap-10 md:gap-14">
      <div class="w-36 shrink-0 md:flex-1">
        <div class="text-6xl font-black">1</div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-2xl">why WHY?</h3>
        <p class="text-sm mt-4 text-neutral-500">
          Since childhood, it has been my favorite question and is the
          foundation for starting any project.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-36 shrink-0 md:flex-1">
        <div class="text-6xl font-black">2</div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-2xl">the BASE</h3>
        <p class="text-sm mt-4 text-neutral-500">
          If you know the why, everything becomes easier. Now, you start to
          structure everything around the why, your own solar system.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-36 shrink-0 md:flex-1">
        <div class="text-6xl font-black">3</div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-2xl">FUN & design</h3>
        <p class="text-sm mt-4 text-neutral-500">
          Now, DESIGN! One of the most fun and chaotic parts, giving meaning to
          everything.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-36 shrink-0 md:flex-1">
        <div class="text-6xl font-black">4</div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-2xl">Make it REAL!</h3>
        <p class="text-sm mt-4 text-neutral-500">
          Seeing a product come to life always amazes and excites me, a tangible
          result of the creative process.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="w-36 shrink-0 md:flex-1">
        <div class="text-6xl font-black">5</div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-2xl">imPROVE</h3>
        <p class="text-sm mt-4 text-neutral-500">
          The end is once again the beginning; it's time to review and improve,
          to learn and be better.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="my-20 mx-6 sm:mx-12" />

  <div class="px-8 sm:px-12 lg:px-24">
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-20 font-bold">my work</div>
    <div class="pt-5 pb-10">
      <div class="md:flex gap-24">
        <div class="md:mb-0 mb-12 md:basis-1/2">
          <h2 class="font-black text-4xl">Peru For Less</h2>
          <div class="max-w-md"></div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-500 max-w-xl font-light">
            I was responsible for redesigning and overseeing the digital
            presence of a brand with over two decades in the market. This brand
            holds a solid position in the tourism industry and{" "}
            <span class="font-bold text-neutral-800">
              is currently ranked as the number one agency globally on
              Trustpilot.
            </span>{" "}
            Additionally, it relies entirely on its digital platform to attract clients.
          </p>
          <div class="pt-10"></div>
          <a
            class="hover:bg-color2 hover:text-white hover:border-color2 transition duration-300 ease-in-out py-4 px-8 border border-neutral-300 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm"
            href="pfl"
          >
            view more
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-0 mb-12 md:basis-1/2 md:w-1/2">
          <CarrouselImage client:only="react" items={ImagePfl} />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-5 pb-10">
      <div class="md:flex gap-24">
        <div class="md:mb-0 mb-12 md:basis-1/2">
          <h2 class="font-black text-4xl">Inca Expert</h2>
          <div class="max-w-md"></div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-500 max-w-xl font-light">
            Inca Expert is one of the highest-rated travel agencies globally,
            according to Trustpilot.{" "}
            <span class="font-bold text-neutral-800">
              I have been responsible for creating, designing, and developing
              this brand.
            </span>{" "}
            From the outset, I set the tone, structure, and design of the website.
            It's a business with a fully digital sales process.
          </p>
          <div class="pt-10"></div>
          <a
            class="hover:bg-color4 hover:text-white hover:border-color4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out py-4 px-8 border border-neutral-300 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm"
            href="inca"
          >
            view more
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-0 mb-12 md:basis-1/2 md:w-1/2">
          <CarrouselImage client:only="react" items={ImageInca} />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-5 pb-10">
      <div class="md:flex gap-24">
        <div class="md:mb-0 mb-12 md:basis-1/2">
          <h2 class="font-black text-4xl">ADA</h2>
          <div class="max-w-md"></div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-500 max-w-xl font-light">
            <span class="font-bold text-neutral-800">
              ADA is the digital gallery showcasing the art and design of
              furniture pieces by the renowned architect Rafael Freyre.
            </span>{" "}
            His creations stand out for their respect for materials and the traditional,
            artisanal processes of various regions in Peru. My role involved translating
            his design vision into the digital platform.
          </p>
          <div class="pt-10"></div>
          <a
            class="hover:bg-neutral-700 hover:text-white hover:border-neutral-700 transition duration-300 ease-in-out py-4 px-8 border border-neutral-300 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm"
            href="ada"
          >
            view more
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-0 mb-12 md:basis-1/2 md:w-1/2">
          <CarrouselImage client:only="react" items={ImageAda} />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- <CarrouselAda client:load /> -->
  </div>

  <hr class="my-20 mx-6 sm:mx-12" />

  <!-- <div class="px-8 sm:px-24 mb-12">
      <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-20 font-bold">
        People I work with
      </div>
      <CarrouselTestimonials client:only="react" items={Testimonials} />
    </div> -->
</Layout>
